title: War of the Roses: A Co-Worker with a Vengeance
description: Carrie works with a guy named Michael who is constantly throwing her under the bus and she recently saw him on Hinge and knows he has a girlfriend.  She dislikes him so much that she is doing War of the Roses out of spite to see if he is cheating.
